race.comment: LADY BLAZINGTON (1) was out of in the placings when eighth last time but prior to that posted a swift 16.82 win over 300m at this track. Hard to top on the time from two back. MISS MOLIK (2) made it two minor placings on the trot when beaten third (17.14) in a Grade 3/4 at this track last time out. Rates a winning chance on best. SECRET NINJA (8) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, hitting the frame latest when 3rd at this track over 300m. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Leading chance. HIGH SCORE (4) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.
